```

## 🚀 如何运行

### 环境要求
1. 安装 [Flutter SDK](https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install)
2. 安装 Android Studio 或配置 Android SDK
3. 安装 JDK 17+

### 运行步骤
```bash
# 克隆项目
git clone https://github.com/your-username/daily_task.git
cd daily_task

# 安装依赖
flutter pub get

# 运行项目
flutter run
```

### 构建APK
```bash
# 构建Release APK
flutter build apk --release
```

生成的APK文件位于：`build/app/outputs/flutter-apk/app-release.apk`

